Descriptions

kz_bhop_666
Original map by CD
Contains 1 course: kz_bhop_666

kz_onlime
Original map by Dydka
Contains 1 course: k_onlime_onlime

kz_onlime_ez
Easier version of kz_onlime (The map is still difficult).

kz_pcm_deathvalley
Original map by Pacman
Contains 2 courses: kz_orange_mountain and kz_2r0cks

kz_pcm_parched
Original map by Pacman
Contains 2 courses: kz_pcm_parched and an unfinished bhop bonus
Notes: Bonus won't work without timer button support (you're meant to jump from the last platform to the button and hit it mid air)

kz_spiritblock_fix
Original map by jYue and SoUlFaThEr
Contains 2 courses: kz_spiritblock and bhop_underground
Notes: this map is already ported to CSS but with the bonus removed, bunch of 64 skips left and a pretty much broken end stage which wasn't tested/adjusted for CSS scale at all.

kz_tabyn
Original map by msl
Contains 1 course: kz_tabyn
